ạ Khúc Thuỷ cử nhân - 擬本縣文會賀曲水舉人</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/Qu%E1%BB%91c-th%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-luDG_JtGJpsmxvdHabA94g">Quốc thương - 國殤</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khu%E1%BA%A5t-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-2RPFDWkSQLaYkT3rYIGIrQ">Khuất Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Mai/Sa-C%C3%A2u/poem-ukvH-iRSLouHNwUae2aIDg">Sa Câu - 沙溝</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Vi%C3%AAn-Mai/author-0wWyWXBTsjFesQNO4r2tUQ">Viên Mai</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Thi%C3%AAn-qu%C3%A2n-th%C3%A1i-nhi%C3%AAn-ph%C3%BA/poem-Le404uILLvNdFLvoYsHNgQ">Thiên quân thái nhiên phú - 天君泰然賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Th%C3%A2n/Y%E1%BA%BFt-Kim-m%C3%B4n/poem-rrp0i3Y_qH-pN6rTEOt_vw">Yết Kim môn - 謁金門</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Th%C3%A2n/author-FbbINXH7lzqgF9ytJv8P4Q">Thái Thân</a>)<br></div>	</div>
